snippet.title: Street Fighter X Mega Man V2 - Enhanced features and A NEW HIDDEN CHARACTER
snippet.description:
Street Fighter X Mega Man V2 has finally arrived with minor tweaks and gameplay enhancements. A new password system, improved controller support, a rebuffed Bison, and what's that... A BRAND NEW SECRET CHARACTER?! All that and more FREE.

Head to http://capcom-unity.com/mega_man to download!
